/**
Mapformat:

- Map Header: 
    -> Size X (1 byte)
    -> Size Y (1 byte)
    -> Mapel Array Bank (1 byte)
    -> Mapel Array address : Address of mapel (2 bytes)
    -> Padding Mapel (1 byte)
    -> Array (x*y)
    
    0                 8                  16
    +------------------+------------------+
    |    Map size X    |   Map size Y     |
    +-------------------------------------+
    | Mapel array Bank |  Mapel Array... 
    +-------------------------------------+
    |    ...address    |  Padding Mapel   |
    +------------------+------------------+
    |                                     |
    +                                     +
    :                Map                  :
    +                                     +
    |                                     |
    +-------------------------------------+ 
*/

